text: Yevgeny Kuzin (born 9 July 1948) is a Russian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male equestrians Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
